The paper proposes a novel method for scene text detection using advanced Convolutional Neural Networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The method is end-to-end trainable and involves the use of machine learning algorithms, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of parallelism and computational efficiency, which are topics in machine learning and optimization (cs.LG). The proposed method involves the use of spatial features and communication mechanisms, which are topics in natural language processing (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
